<div class="container success">
    <div class="container-header">Template Usage Instructions</div>
    <div class="container-content">
        <div class="container-content-inner">
            <h3>How to Use This Template</h3>
            <div class="instruction-grid">
                <div class="instruction-card">
                    <h4>1. Replace Placeholders</h4>
                    <p>Replace all [PLACEHOLDER] values with system-specific information:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>[SYSTEM_NAME] - Name of your system</li>
                        <li>[SYSTEM_DESCRIPTION] - Brief description</li>
                        <li>[PRIMARY_TABLE_NAME] - Main database table</li>
                        <li>[DATA_TYPE] - Primary data type managed</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="instruction-card">
                    <h4>2. Create Sub-Documents</h4>
                    <p>Create the referenced .tt files in appropriate directories:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Documentation/controllers/</li>
                        <li>Documentation/models/</li>
                        <li>Documentation/admin/</li>
                        <li>Documentation/roles/</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="instruction-card">
                    <h4>3. Update Navigation</h4>
                    <p>Customize the Quick Navigation section to match your system's specific sections and anchor links.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="instruction-card">
                    <h4>4. Version Control</h4>
                    <p>Update the PageVersion at the top with your system's file path and version information.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="back-to-top">
    <p id="return_top"><a href="#system_top">Return to Top</a></p>
</div>